Revolutionize Patient Care With Home Health

Enhance patient engagement, improve care coordination, and promote efficient health monitoring with the new Home Health Patient Visits lightning component. With this component available on an Experience cloud site, patients can easily connect with their home health agency and access their past, current, and upcoming home visits from their personal devices.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with the Health Cloud and the Home Health add-on licenses.

Who: This feature is available to users with the Home Health Patient permission set license.

How: Enable Digital Experiences. Build an Experience cloud site and then place the Home Health Patient Visits component on the home page. Use Sharing Settings to create sharing rules for customer portal users and partner users.
